---

<!-- Hero Section -->
<header class="relative w-full mb-20 overflow-hidden pt-20">
  <!-- Gradient overlay left side -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
    <div
      class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-background via-background/80 to-transparent z-10"
    >
    </div>
    <img
      src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida/ADBb0uih-2XsKGcgQTJdme95rwZ9xZeFO3MnaIPCUcJGI5GWnZmy_MdX5Rek6hvNAd6pDfBG5szyOIJegxqBEKxfucRd_Tx2LQLeO7fb7w6jHUp23xZMJmX3IFwLUyHVRd4yLkNtVMVG5BxpttR4RDylEsm1Yr-VS6F-TKaIzDOzOlw-lPlTQW65qoJ3-595g8LjkuFdkmX9jqG5Yy7Kcy8I25lrls9POdxKdm9g_INwKIa0LkFkgdnd_l5hhHn97DIWiRvxdk2awqlJzA"
      alt="Culto na Igreja"
      class="absolute right-0 top-0 h-full w-2/3 object-cover object-center"
      loading="eager"
      fetchpriority="high"
    />
  </div>

  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8 relative z-20 pt-16">
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-end gap-12">
      <div class="flex-1 py-12">
        <h1 class="noto-serif text-5xl md:text-7xl text-primary font-bold mb-6 leading-tight">
          Aqui falamos de
          <br />
          <span
            style="font-family: 'Dancing Script', cursive; font-size: 1.3em; color: #775a19; display: block; margin-top: 0.2em; line-height: 1;"
          >
            esperança!
          </span>
        </h1>
        <p class="manrope text-lg text-on-surface-variant max-w-xl leading-relaxed">
          Seja bem-vindo à nossa comunidade no bairro Niterói, em Canoas.<br />
          Viva aqui momentos dedicados ao louvor, estudo e serviço.<br />
          Nossas portas e corações estão abertos para você. Venha adorar conosco!
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>
